         <div type="translation" resp="part:vito">
             <p>Success! Homage to the Bhagavant! The image of the Buddha Śākyamuni has been established. <supplied reason="subaudible">It was</supplied> commissioned by Radhā, the eminent wife of Muthikumāra <supplied reason="subaudible">and by her</supplied> daughter Khandagopī (Skt. Skandagopī), the wife of Duhasenakumāra (Skt. Dṛḍhasenakumāra), for the good and well-being of the whole world.</p>
         </div>
